An explanation of environment variables for later reference:


https://medium.com/chingu/an-introduction-to-environment-variables-and-how-to-use-them-f602f66d15fa

Env variables are setup in a .env file and are formatted as name=values.
This isnt a feature of either the browser or JS so a package like dotenv is required to enable this (create-react-app has this build in!)